The paper deals with cost-sensitive learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes a framework for achieving minimax classifier over multiple cost matrices. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
